1
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,400
Are you drawing

2
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,890
the palace defense map?

3
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:17,200
I don't know what you are talking about.

4
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:18,680
Ling Xuele.

5
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,490
I didn't know Prince Wuyu was here.

6
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:31,320
I hope I didn't spoil your mood, Your Highness.

7
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,440
Lady Anli.

8
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,760
I came to visit the First Prince,

9
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,890
but unfortunately,

10
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,410
he has not returned yet.

11
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,560
So I'm just waiting here for a while.

12
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:40,760
May I ask why Lady Anli

13
00:02:41,079 --> 00:02:42,840
brought these people here?

14
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,560
Prince Wuyu,

15
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:47,420
are you really waiting for His Highness?

16
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,980
Please forgive my bluntness.

17
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,320
This girl

18
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:53,920
was seen having an affair with a guard at the palace gate yesterday,

19
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:56,650
and today she is alone with you in this courtyard.

20
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,079
What her intentions are,

21
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:02,280
I'm sure you know very well.

22
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:03,880
When did I...

23
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:04,720
Lady Anli,

24
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:06,450
what you said

25
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:09,160
might be slandering Lady Xuele's reputation.

26
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:12,100
Whether it's a slander or not,

27
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,850
a search will reveal the truth.

28
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,400
Search!

29
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,320
Yes.

30
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,120
Lady Anli.

31
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,079
Lady Anli!

32
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,010
This is Yuze Palace.

33
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,520
Without His Highness's permission,

34
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,250
how can you trespass like this?

35
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:30,810
You secretly had an affair with a royal guard,

36
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:33,140
which is already a serious crime.

37
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:35,980
I am just cleaning up the house for His Highness.

38
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,000
What?

39
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,650
Are you feeling guilty?

40
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,480
Search carefully.

41
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:53,320
Don't miss a single corner.

42
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:09,370
Since when is my Yuze Palace so lively?

43
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:11,980
Brother Yunchuan!

44
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,560
Lady Anli.

45
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,050
Prince Wuyu is here too.

46
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,380
Brother Yunchuan,

47
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,560
I accidentally caught this maid

48
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,240
acting suspiciously in the palace,

49
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:25,720
and being very intimate with a guard.

50
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,160
I was worried

51
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:29,720
that it would damage your reputation if word got out,

52
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,680
so I took the liberty to come today

53
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,240
to find out the truth.

54
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:35,800
Lady Anli,

55
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,840
since when did my little maid in Yuze Palace

56
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:38,970
concern you so much?

57
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,040
I acted inappropriately.

58
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:46,240
Please forgive me, Brother Yunchuan.

59
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,960
Lady Anli kept saying

60
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,960
that Lady Xuele had an affair with someone,

61
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:52,000
and just implied that she seduced me.

62
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,640
Since His Highness has returned,

63
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:55,280
why not investigate it thoroughly?

64
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,280
If it's true,

65
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:58,080
you can punish her yourself.

66
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,800
If it's just a misunderstanding,

67
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,200
it will stop the gossips.

68
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,760
After all, this is no trivial matter.

69
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:05,800
If someone uses it to make up stories,

70
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,730
it will also damage my reputation.

71
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,370
Then, Lady Anli,

72
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:15,040
did you find anything?

73
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,640
Found it!

74
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,880
You are so panicked.

75
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,120
It seems

76
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,680
this is the evidence of your affair.

77
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,720
This is clearly given to you by that guard

78
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,720
as a token of love.

79
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:38,300
What else do you have to say for yourself?

80
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,360
I...

81
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:50,960
As for this painting,

82
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:52,530
I painted it myself.

83
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,800
A few days ago,

84
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,840
when I was confined to the palace,

85
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:00,840
I had nothing to do,

86
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,370
so I just drew a few strokes.

87
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,120
Didn't I

88
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:06,040
tell you to throw it away?

89
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,100
Why did you keep it?

90
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,580
Your Highness.

91
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,880
Although you drew it casually,

92
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:16,280
but

93
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,160
you painted it yourself.

94
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:21,800
And this portrait looks like me.

95
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,760
I was afraid if it wasn't kept properly,

96
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:26,720
it might cause trouble for Your Highness,

97
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,360
so I put it away for now.

98
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:32,080
You are quite thoughtful.

99
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,400
Lady Anli,

100
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,600
it seems to be a misunderstanding.

101
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,130
Apologize to Lady Anli now.

102
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,159
I acted recklessly

103
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:46,340
and caused Lady Anli to worry.

104
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:47,000
You...

105
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,440
Lady Anli.

106
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,360
The servants in the palace

107
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,360
are not sensible.

108
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:52,130
Another day,

109
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,140
I will visit you to apologize.

110
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,100
How about that?

111
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:01,080
I have offended you today.

112
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,080
Since it's a misunderstanding,

113
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:04,840
I will take my leave now.

114
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,560
I think Lady Anli

115
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:22,160
has ulterior motives towards Your Highness.

116
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,840
Once a woman gets jealous,

117
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,740
she becomes hard to deal with.

118
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,720
Brother Wuyu,

119
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,650
please don't make fun of me.

120
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:32,040
I came here this time

121
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:34,040
wanting to chat with Your Highness,

122
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:36,140
but running into this ruined my mood.

123
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:38,240
I found some good wine recently.

124
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,400
If you have time, Ruochuan,

125
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,960
you can come over to my place.

126
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,220
I'll take my leave now.

127
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,960
Definitely, some other day.

128
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,370
About what happened today,

129
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,440
how do you explain it?

130
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,220
Your Highness.

131
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:20,280
I have never done anything shameful.

132
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,000
I naturally believe you,

133
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:28,020
which is why I want to hear your explanation.

134
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:31,480
The maid who came to me yesterday

135
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:34,010
is well acquainted with the guard.

136
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,200
So,

137
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,200
she introduced him to me,

138
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,880
just thinking that transporting clothes into the palace

139
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:42,080
would be more convenient in the future.

140
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,559
But I didn't expect

141
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,760
Lady Anli to see it.

142
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,320
That maid

143
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:50,560
is named Chunlan,

144
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,730
working in the Laundry Bureau.

145
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:53,640
That guard

146
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,680
is named Cangyu,

147
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:57,280
on duty by the North Gate.

148
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,800
If Your Highness doesn't believe me,

149
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:02,280
I can call them to testify.

150
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,960
However,

151
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:06,120
sneaking things into the palace

152
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,380
is a serious crime.

153
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,440
If I force them to answer,

154
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:12,770
they definitely won't tell the truth.

155
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:15,840
Please see clearly, Your Highness.

156
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,120
Then who painted that portrait?

157
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,520
That portrait

158
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:25,080
was indeed previously painted by me

159
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,840
for the fabric workshop.

160
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,730
It's not a token of love.

161
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,520
Do you know

162
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,840
the clothes in that portrait

163
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,280
are from Xuecang?

164
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,760
If someone else were here today,

165
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:39,360
even I

166
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:40,980
couldn't save you.

167
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:46,290
Forgive me, Your Highness.

168
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:48,360
I wouldn't dare to deceive you, Your Highness.

169
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:50,280
I was born into a merchant family.

170
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:51,880
Since I was young,

171
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:54,330
I have traveled around with my father.

172
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,770
The clothes in the portrait

173
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,680
were drawn when I passed through the Northern Border,

174
00:09:58,680 --> 00:10:00,880
based on their local clothing customs.

175
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:03,120
It was my negligence.

176
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:06,810
I shouldn't have kept this portrait secretly in the palace.

177
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:12,280
From now on,

178
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,800
I will be extremely careful.

179
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:20,440
All right,

180
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:21,520
get up.

181
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,900
Just be careful in the future.

182
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:51,960
Anli comes to pay respects to you, Aunt.

183
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:55,800
Aunt.

184
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:56,680
Kneel.

185
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:58,600
Aunt.

186
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,680
I don't know what I did wrong.

187
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,120
Recently,

188
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,820
you seem to go to Yuze Palace a lot.

189
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:08,220
I remember your teachings, Aunt,

190
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:10,600
so I want to get closer to His Highness,

191
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:11,760
to live up to

192
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:13,840
your painstaking cultivation.

193
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:16,520
Who said the position of Crown Prince will definitely be his?

194
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:19,000
That jinx doesn't have such good luck.

195
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,520
Aunt, do you mean...

196
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:26,440
If you are a smart person,

197
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:28,880
you naturally know what I am saying.

198
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:30,860
If you can't figure it out,

199
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:33,680
I will arrange for someone tomorrow

200
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:35,360
to send you back to Baishi.

201
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:37,880
I understand.

202
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,240
In the future,

203
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,660
I will follow your teachings.

204
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:42,930
You understand?

205
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,680
Good.

206
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,360
I

207
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:50,060
am going to serve His Majesty.

208
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,260
Kneel for another hour

209
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,200
to learn your lesson.

210
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:06,440
Aunt.

211
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,640
You said it too late.

212
00:12:10,040 --> 00:12:12,500
I have already fallen in love with Yunchuan.

213
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:31,480
Pingle.

214
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,770
Don't be afraid.

215
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,130
I am here to help you.

216
00:12:34,760 --> 00:12:36,020
I don't need your help.

217
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,440
Give me back the palace defense map.

218
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:40,840
Pingle.

219
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:44,200
I have given the defense map to someone who needs it more.

220
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,730
Just wait for the good show.

221
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:53,740
Your Highness.

222
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:58,000
Ling Xuele's household register in the palace

223
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,460
was indeed tampered with.

224
00:12:59,560 --> 00:13:01,160
The woman originally conscripted into the palace

225
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:02,020
is named Liu Xu,

226
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,560
an ordinary peasant.

227
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:04,880
I just didn't expect

228
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:06,040
that this household register,

229
00:13:06,040 --> 00:13:07,880
which even Your Highness cannot easily touch,

230
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,440
how could she have such ability?

231
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,300
Your Highness,

232
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:11,920
I think

233
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:14,680
you should send Miss Xuele away from the palace.

234
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:15,120
No.

235
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:19,770
Don't tell me you have feelings for Miss Xuele...

236
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:22,580
What nonsense are you talking about?

237
00:13:23,560 --> 00:13:24,240
Keep her.

238
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:25,640
I have other uses for her.

239
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:27,520
Qi Beiyi is rebelling!

240
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:30,200
Qi Beiyi is storming the palace!

241
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:31,240
Your Highness,

242
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,160
it's chaotic outside.

243
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,080
Go see what happened.

244
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:33,520
Yes.

245
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:35,720
Protect His Majesty!

246
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:36,560
Guards!

247
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:37,640
Assassins!

248
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:38,960
Fire!

249
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:45,000
Get in.

250
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:38,860
Your Highness,

251
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,080
you're awake.

252
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:44,840
Help me up.

253
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:45,920
Okay.

254
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:47,240
Here,

255
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:48,320
here,

256
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:49,460
be careful.

257
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,980
I'll pour you a glass of water.

258
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,480
Why are you alone?

259
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:01,880
Here, Your Highness.

260
00:15:01,880 --> 00:15:03,010
Where is Ling Xuele?

261
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:05,360
Was she hurt?

262
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,960
She... she's fine.

263
00:15:13,400 --> 00:15:14,640
By the way, Your Highness,

264
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:17,000
the matter of the rebels setting fire and assassinating last night

265
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,330
has been investigated.

266
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:20,500
It was actually Qi Beiyi's doing.

267
00:15:21,280 --> 00:15:22,810
He betrayed Xuecang first,

268
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:25,240
and now he came to assassinate His Majesty.

269
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,520
What a treacherous villain.

270
00:15:26,520 --> 00:15:27,580
He deserves to die.

271
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:29,120
My father inciting Qi Beiyi's defection

272
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:30,880
to wipe out Xuecang,

273
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:33,080
he only mentioned it to me in private.

274
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,880
Xuele probably doesn't know yet.

275
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,400
But he defected again last night,

276
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:38,260
so Xuele must have heard about it.

277
00:15:38,640 --> 00:15:39,700
Where is Xuele now?

278
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:45,480
She is injured

279
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:46,900
and is resting now.

280
00:15:51,800 --> 00:15:53,260
You just said she was fine,

281
00:15:54,040 --> 00:15:55,700
and now you say she's injured.

282
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:57,200
What exactly is going on?

283
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:02,640
Your Highness,

284
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:04,440
when Qi Beiyi was escaping,

285
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:05,600
Ling Xuele ran out.

286
00:16:05,920 --> 00:16:08,040
Qi Beiyi shouted that she was the Princess of Xuecang.

287
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:08,640
Right now,

288
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:10,920
she has been thrown into prison.

289
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:12,920
What?
